Shooting stars *

44:20.358 --> 44:21.693
We're gonna make a run for it.

44:21.727 --> 44:22.961
* Live for glory, not forever *

44:22.994 --> 44:27.398
-Go!
-* Reach out *

44:27.432 --> 44:31.002
